### 3. Download Error CSV (use errorCSV from previous response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/upload/v2/download-errors
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "errorCSV": "row_number,Sem,Br,FacultyN,EnrolN,Name,Semester,Hall,SPI,CPI,CumEC,Result,error_message\n3,S2221,,18CE002,GK1002,Jane Smith,4,Hall B,9.0,8.8,60,Pass,\"Missing branch code\"\n4,S2221,CE,,GK1003,Bob Wilson,0,Hall C,7.5,7.8,55,Pass,\"Missing faculty number; Invalid semester\"\n5,S2221,CE,18CE004,,Alice Brown,4,Hall D,8.0,8.5,58,Pass,\"Missing enrollment number\""
}

### Expected: CSV file download with failed rows

